archimate:ApplicationFunction.name: Service Test result interpretation policies management
archimate:ApplicationFunction.documentation: Service Test Strategy and Policy Management interpretation of test results functions provide the necessary functionality to manage how the test results should be interpreted. Strategies can range from simple (e.g. - check the status of a router) to complex (e.g. - perform an end-to-end test on a circuit and sectionalize the problem).
